hadiths[171]{hadithnumber,text}:
1845,"Hazrat Alqama bin Qais (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Mina mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key sath tha ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) unhen alag ley gaey, main paas betha tha. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey farmaya : kya aap pasand farmatey hain ke main eik kanwari ladki sey aap ki shaadi karwa dun jis sey aap ko guzrey waqt ki kuch baaten yad aa jaeyn ? jab Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko mehsus huwa ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko uskey siwa aur koi kaam nahin (jis key liye wo unhen alag ley gaey they) to mujhey haath sey ishara kya. mein hazir huwa to wo farma rahey they : agar aap ney ye baat kahi hai to ( achi baat hi ki hai kyonkey) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey jawaanon ki jamaat ! tum mein sey jo shakhs nikah ki taqat rakhta hai, usey chahiye ke shaadi kar ley , uski wajeh sey nazar neechi rehti hai aur jism ( badkaari sey) mehfooz rehta hai. aur jisey (nikah ki) taqat na ho to usey chahiye ke roza rakhey kyonkey roza, khahish ko kuchal deta hai."
1846,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nikah mera tariqa hai. aur jo shakhs merey tariqey par amal nahin karta, uska mujh sey talluq nahin. Shadiyan kiya karo kyonkey main tumhari kasrat ki bina par dusri ummaton par fakhr karunga, jo (maali tor par) istataat rakhta ho wo ( zarur) nikah karey aur jisey ( rishta) na miley , wo rozey rakha karey kyonkey roza khahish ko kuchal deta hai."
1847,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aapas mein mohabbat rakhney walon key liye nikah jaisi koi chiz nahin dekhi gaee."
1848,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Usman bin Maazun (Raziallahu anhu) ko be-nikah rehney ki ijazat nahin di. agar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen ijazat dey detey to hum log khassi ho jatey."
1849,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney be-nikah rehney sey mana farmaya. Zaid bin Akhzam ney ye izafa bhi bayan kiya hai ke Hazrat Qatada (Rahimahullah) ney (is masley ko wazeh karney key liye) ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (وَلَقَدْ أَرْ سَلْنَا رُ سُلًا مِّن قَبْلِكَ وَجَعَلْنَا لَهُمْ أَزْوَ جًا وَذُرّ يَّةً ۚ),''aur yaqinan hamney aap sey pehley Rasool bhejey aur in ko biwiyon aur auladon wala banaya.''"
1850,"Hazrat Hakim bin Muawiya apney walid Hazrat Muawiya (ibne-Haida (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya : khawind par aurat ka kya haq hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab khana khaye to usey bhi khilaaey, jab kapda pehney to usey bhi pahnaaey, chehrey par na maarey, usey bura bhala na kahey aur ghar hi mein (us sey) alehdgi ikhtiyar kiye rakhey."
1851,"Hazrat Amr bin Ahwas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Hijjatul-wadaa mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath mojud they. (us doran mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Allah ki hamd aur sanaa ki, aur waaz aur nasihat farmaai. (is mein aap ney kaee baaten irshad farmaeen) phir farmaya : aurton key barey mein khair ki wasiyat qubul karo kyonkey wo tumharey paas qaidi (madadgaar) hain. tumhen un par iskey siwa koi ikhtiyar nahin. agar ye ke wo wazeh be-sharmi ka koi kaam karen. agar wo aisi harkat karen to un sey bistaron mein alag ho jao, aur unhen maaro lekin sakht pitaai na ho. (is tanbih key natijey mein) agar wo tumhari itaat karney lag jaeyn to un par (sakhti karney ki) raah talash na karo yaqinan tumhari aurton par tumhara haq hai, aur tumhari aurton ka tum par haq hai. tumhari aurton par tumhara haq to ye hai ke wo tumharey bistaron par usey na bithaaey jis (key ghar mein aaney) ko tum napasand kartey ho, aur tumharey ghar mein us fard ko aaney ki ijazat na den jisey tum napasand kartey ho. suno ! tum par aurton ka ye haq hai ke unkey libas aur khurak key barey mein un sey achchha sulook karo."
1852,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar main kisi ko hukm deta ke kisi insan ko sajda karey to aurat ko hukm deta ke wo apney khawind ko sajda karey. agar koi mard aurat ko hukm dey ke surkh pahad sey (patthar utha kar) siyah pahad par ley jaey, aur siyah pahad sey surkh pahad par ley jaey to aurat key liye yehi munasib hai ke wo ye kaam karey."
1853,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Sham sey aaye to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sajda kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Muaz ! ye kya? unhoney kaha : main Sham gaya to mainey wahan key logon ko dekha ke wo apney paadriyon aur sardaron ko sajda kartey hain. mujhey apney dil mein ye baat achchhi lagi ke hum log aap key sath (tazeem aur ehtiraam ka) ye tariqa ikhtiyar karen to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum (ye kaam) na karo. agar main kisi ko Allah key siwa kisi key liye sajda karney ka hukm deta to aurat ko hukm deta ke apney khawind ko sajda kiya kerey. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! aurat apney Rab ka haq ada nahin kar sakti, jab tak apney khawind ka haq ada nahin karti agar wo oont key kajawey par bethi hui ho aur khawind us sey khahish ka izhar karey to usey inkar nahin karna chahiye."
1854,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : jo aurat is haal mein faut hui ke uska khawind us sey khush tha to wo jannat mein jaeygi.
1855,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya (aarzi) faaedey ki chiz hai aur duniya key saazo saman mein nek aurat sey behtar koi chiz nahin."
1856,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab soney chaandi key barey mein hukm nazil huwa to Sahaba kiram ney (aapas mein) kaha : hum kon sa maal hasil keren? Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main tumhen ye (masla) malum kar key batata hun. unhoney apney oont ko tez chalaya, yahan tak key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunch gaey. (Soban farmatey hain : ) main bhi unkey peechhey peechhey tha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kon sa maal hasil (kerney ki koshish) keren? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhen chahiye ke shukar karney wala dil hasil karo aur zikr karney wali zaban, aur momin biwi jo aakhirat key maamlat mein mard ki madad karey."
1857,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : momin ko Allah key taqwe key baad nek biwi sey behtar koi chiz nahin mil sakti. (aisi biwi ke) jab wo usey koi hukm dey to wo uski taameel karey, jab uski taraf nazar utha kar dekhey to usey khush kar dey, agar usey koi qism dey to wo qism puri kar dey, agar wo uski nazron sey ojhal ho (safar waghera mein chala jaey) to apni zaat key barey mein aur uskey maal key barey mein us sey mukhlis rahey (khayanat na kerey)."
1858,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurton sey chaar chizon ki wajeh sey nikah kiya jata hai : (kisi sey) uskey maal ki wajeh sey, (kisi sey) uskey hasab aur nasab ki wajeh sey, ( kisi sey) uskey Husn aur jamaal ki wajeh sey, (kisi sey) uski deendaari (aur neki) ki wajeh sey. to Deen daar aurat (key husool mein) kamiyab ho ja. tera bhala ho."
1859,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurton sey unkey Husn ki wajeh sey nikah na karo, mumkin hai unka Husn unhen (takabbur mein mubtala kar key) tabah kar dey , un sey unkey maal ki wajeh sey nikah na karo, mumkin hai unka maal unhen sarkash bana (kar gunahon mein mubtala kar) dey , albatta unkey Deen ko peshe-nazar rakhtey huye nikah koiya karo. eik siyah rang, naak-kati, deen-daar londi (khoobsurat, be-deen azad aurat sey) afzal hai."
1860,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamanae Mubarak mein , mainey eik khatoon sey nikah kiya. (uskey baad jab) meri mulaqat Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey hui to aap ney farmaya : Jabir ! kya aap ney shaadi kar li? mainey kaha : ji haan ! aap ney farmaya : kanwari sey ya bewa sey? mainey kaha : bewa sey. farmaya : kanwari sey kyon na ki jis sey tum dil behlaate? mainey kaha : meri kaee behney thin. mujhey dar mehsus huwa ke wo merey aur unkey darmiyan haael (rukawat) na ho jaaey. aap ney farmaya : tab ye baat (durust hai)."
1861,"Hazrat Utba bin Uwaim bin Saaida Ansari (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kunwaariyon sey nikah karo kyonkey wo sheereen dahan (ziyada hayadaar), ziyada bachchey paida karney wali , aur thodi chiz par razi rehney wali hoti hain."
1862,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs pak saaf ho kar Allah sey mulaqat karna chahta hai, usey chahiye ke azad aurton sey nikah karey."
1863,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nikah karo, main tumhari kasrat par fakhr karunga."
1864,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Salma (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey eik aurat ko nikah ka pegham diya. main us (ko dekhney) key liye chhup jaya karta tha yahan tak key mainey usey uskey khajuron key baagh mein dekh liya. (haazirin mein sey) kisi ney kaha : aap Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba ho kar bhi aisa kartey hain? unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna hai : jab Allah Taala kisi shakhs key dil mein kisi aurat sey nikah ki khahish daley to usey dekh leney mein koi harj nahin."
1865,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik khatoon sey nikah karney ka irada kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : ja kar usey dekh lo, ummid hai ke tum dono mein muwaafiqat (razamandi) paida ho jaeygi. unhoney aisey hi kiya, phir us sey shaadi kar li. iskey baad unhoney us sey muwaafiqat ka zikr farmaya."
1866,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar eik khatoon ka zikr kya ke main us sey nikah key liye pegham bhejney wala hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ja kar usey dekh lo , ummid hai tumharey darmiyan mohabbat paida ho jaeygi . chunanche main eik Ansari khatoon key yahan gaya aur uskey waliden sey uska rishta talab kya aur unhen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka irshad bhi sunaya. yun mehsus huwa ke uskey waliden ney us chiz ko pasand nahin kya (ke ye mard us ladki ko dekhay.) ladki pardey mein thi, usney ye baat cheet sun li, chunanche usney kaha : agar tujhey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dekhney ka hukm diya hai to dekh ley warna mein tujhey qism deti hun (ke jhoota bahana bana kar mujhey na dekhna) usney goya is baat ko bahut bada samjha (suntey hi aetbar na aaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hoga (Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : ( mein sach keh raha tha, isliye ) mainey usey dekh liya , phir mainey us sey shaadi kar li . phir Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey hum-aahangi paida ho janey ka zikr farmaya."
1867,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi aadmi apney bhai key pegham nikah par nikah ka pegham na bhejey."
1868,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi aadmi apney bhai key peghame-nikah par nikah ka pegham na bhejey."
1869,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujh sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab teri iddat khatam ho jaey to mujhey batana. (iddat khatam honey par) unhoney aap ko ittilaa di. unhen Hazrat Muawiya , abu-Jahm bin sikhkhir aur Hazrat Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhum ney nikah key liye pegham bhejey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) to muflis aadmi hain, unkey paas maal nahin, abu-Jahm (Raziallahu anhu) aurton ko bahut maartay hain lekin Usama ( (Raziallahu anhu) behtareen hain.) Hazrat Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu anha) ney haath sey is tarah ishara kar key kaha : Usama ! Usama ! Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki itaat aur uskey Rasool ki itaat terey liye behtar hai. 'Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan kya : mainey un sey nikah kar liya, phir mujh par rashk kya gaya ."
1870,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shohar wali apni zaat par apney wali (sarparast) sey ziyada ikhtiyar rakhti hai. aur kanwari sey uski zaat key barey mein ijazat li jaey. arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! kanwari baat kartey huye sharmati hai. aap ney farmaya : uski khamoshi hi uski ijazat hai."
1871,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shohar deeda ka nikah us sey mashwara kiye baghair na kya jaey. aur kanwari ka nikah us sey ijazat liye baghair na kya jaey. aur uski ijazat khamosh rehna hai."
1872,"Hazrat Adi bin Adi kandi (Rahimahullah) apney walid Hazrat Adi bin umaira (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey huye farmatey hain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shohar deeda apni raza-mandi ka (zaban sey) izhar karey aur kanwari ki raza-mandi (ki alamat) uska khamosh rehna hai."
1873,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed Ansari aur Hazrat majmaa bin Yazeed Ansari (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unkey khandan key eik shakhs Hazrat Khizam (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni beti ka nikah kar diya. usney apney walid key kiye huye nikah ko pasand na kya, chunanche usney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar waqia arz kya. aap ney uskey walid ka kya huwa nikah kal-adam qarar dey diya . tab usney Hazrat abu-Lubaba bin abdul-munzir (Raziallahu anhu) sey nikah kar liya . Hazrat Yahya bin Saeed (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ye ladki Sayyeb (bewa ya Talaq yafta) thi."
1874,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida (Rahimahullah) apney walid Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : eik nojawan ladki ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : merey walid ney mera nikah apney bhatijey sey kar diya hai taake merey zariey sey uska maqam buland ho jaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ladki ko (nikah fasakh karney ka) ikhtiyar dey diya. usney kaha : main apney walid key kiye huye nikah ko qubul karti hun lekin main chahti thi ke aurton ko malum ho jaey ke unkey baapon ko koi ikhtiyar hasil nahin."
1875,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik kanwari ladki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur bataya ke uskey walid ney uska nikah kar diya hai jabke wo (us rishtey sey) na khush hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey (nikah qaaim rakhney ya na rakhney ka) ikhtiyar dey diya . eik dusri sanad sey bhi ye riwayat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey isi tarah marvi hai.
1876,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mera nikah huwa to meri umr chhe saal thi . hum (hijrat kar key) Madina aaye to banu Haris bin khazraj key mohalley mein thehrey. (eik baar aisa huwa ke) mujhey bukhar aaya to merey sar key baal jhad gaey yahan tak key kandhon tak lataktey huye thodey sey baal reh gaey. (eik din) mein jhula jhul rahi thi aur merey sath chand saheliyaan bhi thin ke meri walida Umme Ruman (Raziallahu anha) ney aa kar mujhey aawaz di. main unkey paas aa gaee . mujhey malum nahin tha ke unka kya irada hai? unhoney mera haath pakda aur ghar key darwazey tak ley aain. mera saans phula huwa tha. (thodi der mein) mera saans kuch theek ho gaya. Ammi jaan ney pani ley kar mera sar munh dhoya, phir mujhey ghar key andar ley gaeen, dekha to ghar mein chand Ansari khawatin mojud thin. unhoney kaha : ( عَلَى الْخَيْرِ وَالْبَرَكَةِ , وَعَلَى خَيْرِ طَائِرٍ ) khair o barkat key sath aao , tumhari qismat achi ho. Ammi jaan ney mujhey un khawatin key hawaley kar diya . unhoney meri haalat ko durust kya (kanghi patti ki aur zeb o zeenat kar key dulhan bana diya .) mujhey tabhi pata chala jab chaasht key waqt Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye aur khawatin ney mujhey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas bhej diya . us waqt meri umr no saal thi ."
1877,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey nikah kya to unki umr saat baras thi aur jab unki rukhsati hui to wo no saal ki thin. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui to ummul-mominin ki umr atthaara saal thi ."
1878,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) eik beti chhod kar faut ho gaey . Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya ke uskey walid ki wafat key baad merey mamu Hazrat qudama (Raziallahu anhu) ney , jo us ladki key chacha they, us sey mashwara liye baghair mujh sey uska nikah kar diya. usney unkey kiye huye rishtey ko pasand na kya. wo chahti thi ke wo uska nikah Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey kartey, chunanche Hazrat Qudama (Raziallahu anhu) ney (pehla nikah fasakh kar key) uska nikah un (Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu)) sey kar diya ."
1879,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aurat ka nikah sar parast ney nahin kya, uska nikah batil hai, uska nikah batil hai, uska nikah batil (kal-adam) hai. agar mard us sey maqaribat kar ley to uski maqaribat ki wajeh sey us aurat ko haq mehar ada kya jaeyga. agar un (sar paraston) mein baham (aapas mein) ikhtilaf ho jaey to jiska koi wali (sar parast) na ho, badshah uska wali (sar-parast) hai."
1880,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sar parast ( ki ijazat) key baghair nikah nahin hota. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki riwayat mein ye alfaz bhi hain : jiska wali na ho, badshah uska wali hai."
1881,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wali (sar parast) key baghair nikah nahin ."
1882,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi aurat kisi aurat ka nikah na kerey. na aurat khud apna nikah kerey. badkaar aurat hi apna nikah khud karti hai."
1883,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nikah shighaar sey mana farmaya hai. aur shighaar ye hai ke eik shakhs doosrey sey kahey : tum mujh sey apni beti ya behan ka nikah kar do, uskey iwaz main tum sey apni beti ya behan ka nikah kar dunga. aur un dono (aurton) ka haq mehar kuch na ho."
1884,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nikah shighaar sey mana farmaya."
1885,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam mein koi shighaar nahin ."
1886,"Hazrat abu-Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaaj mutahraat ka haq mehar kitna tha? unhoney farmaya : aapki azwaaj mutahraat ka haq mehar baara auqiya aur nash tha. kya tujhey malum hai nash kya hota hai? wo aadha auqiya hota hai. ye (kul miqdaar) paanch so dirham hai."
1887,"Hazrat Abul-Ajfaa Sulami (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aurton key haq mehar mein ghulw na karo, agar ye kaam ( bahut ziyada haq mehar muqarrar karna ) duniya mein izzat ka baais hota , ya Allah key yahan taqwa (aur neki ka kaam shumar) hota to Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ziyada haq rakhtey they ke aisa kartey . baara auqiya sey ziyada na Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni kisi zauja mohtarma ko haq mehar diya aur na aap ki kisi beti ko mila. aadmi apni biwi key liye bahut ziyada haq mehar muqarrar kar leta hai. baad mein uskey dil mein biwi sey nafrat ka baais bin jata hai. aur wo kehta hai : mainey terey liye mishkizey ki rassi uthai. ya mushk ka paseena bardasht kya. Abul-Ajfaa (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : main Arab mein paida hua tha, (isliye is muhawrey ko samajh nahin saka.) malum nahin 'mushk ki rassi' ya 'mushk ka pasina', iska kya matlab hai."
1888,Hazrat Aamir bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke qabila banu Fazara key eik aadmi ney jooton ka joda haq mehar muqarrar kar key nikah kya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey nikah ko sahih qarar dey diya .
1889,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke eik khatoon Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is sey kon nikah kerega? eik aadmi ney kaha : main. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey farmaya : usey (haq mehar) do, chahey lohey ki angoothi ho. usney kaha : merey paas (lohey ki anguthi bhi) nahin hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey jo Quran yad hai mainey uskey iwaz uska nikah tujh sey kar diya ."
1890,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghar ka kuch saman haq mehar muqarrar kar key Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey nikah farmaya. us saman ki qeemat pachas dirham thi .
1891,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke un sey us shakhs key mutalliq daryaft kya gaya jisney eik aurat sey nikah kya aur khilwat sey pehley faut ho gaya aur usney haq mehar ka tayun bhi nahin kya tha. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya is ko haq mehar bhi milega aur (khaawind ki) meeras bhi milegi aur usey iddat bhi guzarni hogi. Hazrat Maaqil bin Sanan Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) ney uth kar farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha ke aap ney Hazrat Birwaa bint Washiq (Raziallahu anha) key mamley mein yehi faisla diya tha. (Imam Ibne-Maja key ustaad) abu-Bakar bin Abu-Sheba ney eik dusri sanad sey Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hi sey mazkura riwayat ki misl bayan kya.
1892,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bhalai ki jaame cheezen aur uski aakhiri cheezen ata huin. ya farmaya : neki key shuru aur aakhir ki cheezen (ya alfaz). chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen namaz ka khutba bhi sikhaya aur hajat ka khutba bhi. namaz ka khutba ye hai : ( التَّحِيَّاتُ لِلَّهِ وَالصَّلَوَاتُ وَالطَّيِّبَاتُ , السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِيُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ , السَّلَامُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ , أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ , وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ ) tamam zabani ibadatein, badani ibadatein aur maali ibadatein Allah key liye hain. aey Nabi! aap par salam ho aur Allah ki rahmatein aur barkaten hon. hum par bhi salamti ho aur Allah key nek bandon par bhi. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. aur khutba hajat ye hai : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ , نَحْمَدُهُ , وَنَسْتَعِينُهُ , وَنَسْتَغْفِرُهُ , وَنَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ مِنْ شُرُورِ أَنْفُسِنَا , وَمِنْ سَيِّئَاتِ أَعْمَالِنَا , مَنْ يَهْدِهِ اللَّهُ فَلَا مُضِلَّ لَهُ , وَمَنْ يُضْلِلْ فَلَا هَادِيَ لَهُ , وَأَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ , وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ )tamam tareef Allah key liye hai, hum uski tareef kartey hain, us sey madad maangtey hain, us sey bakhshish maangtey hain, hum apney nafson ki shararaton sey aur apney aamal ki buraiyon sey Allah ki panah mein aatey hain. jisey Allah hidayat dey, usey koi gumrah karney wala nahin aur jisey Allah Taala gumrah rehney dey usey koi raah dikhaney wala nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin jis ka koi shareek nahin . aur main gawahi deta hun ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. phir khutbey mein kitabullah ki ye teen aayaat bhi padhin : ( يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ ٱتَّقُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ حَقَّ تُقَاتِهِۦ وَلَا تَمُوتُنَّ إِلَّا وَأَنتُم مُّسْلِمُونَ )' aey eman walo ! Allah sey daro , jaisey us sey darney ka haq hai aur tumhen maut na aaye magar us haalat mein ke tum musalman ho.( يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّاسُ ٱتَّقُوا۟ رَبَّكُمُ ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَكُم مِّن نَّفْسٍ وَحِدَةٍ وَخَلَقَ مِنْهَا زَوْجَهَا وَبَثَّ مِنْهُمَا رِجَالًا كَثِيرا وَنِسَآءً وَٱتَّقُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ ٱلَّذِى تَسَآءَلُونَ بِهِ وَٱلْأَرْحَامَ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ كَانَ عَلَيْكُمْ رَقِيبًا ) aey logo! apney rab sey daro jisney tumhen eik jaan sey paida kya aur usi sey uska joda paida kar key un dono sey mard aur aurten kasrat sey phela diye. aur us Allah sey daro jis key naam sey tum eik doosrey sey maangtey ho. aur rishtey natey todney sey bacho, beshak Allah tum par nigehban hai.( يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ ٱتَّقُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ وَقُولُوا۟ قَوْلًا سَدِيدًا يُصْلِحْ لَكُمْ أَعْمَـٰلَكُمْ وَيَغْفِرْلَكُمْ ذُنُوبَكُمْ وَمَن يُطِعِ ٱللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُۥ فَقَدْ فَازَ فَوْزًا عَظِيمًا ) aey wo logo jo eman laye ho Allah sey daro, aur sidhi (do took aur sachi) baat kaho. wo (Allah) tumharey kaam sanwaar dega, aur tumharey gunah maaf farma dega aur jo koi Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat karey to yaqinan usney badi kamiyabi hasil kar li."
1893,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( الحمدلله نحمده . . .) sab taarifein Allah key liye hain, hum uski hamd kartey hain, us sey madad maangtey hain. aur hum apney nafson ki shararaton sey aur apney aamal ki burai sey uski panah mein aatey hain. jisey Allah hidayat dey usey koi gumrah karney wala nahin aur jisey Allah hidayat sey mehroom rakhey usey koi hidayat deney wala nahin. main gawahi deta hun ke akeley Allah key siwa koi maabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, aur ye ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. amma baad ."
1894,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ahmiyat wala har wo kaam be barkat hai jisey Allah ki tareef sey shuru na kya jaey."
1895,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is nikah ka aelan kya karo aur us moqey par daf bajaya karo."
1896,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : halal aur haram mein farq nikah key moqey par daf aur buland aawaz ka hai."
1897,"Hazrat abu-Husain Khalid madni (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Aashoora key din hum Madina mein they. ladkiyan daf baja rahi thin aur geet ga rahi thin. hum Hazrat Rabee binte-muawwiz (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur unhen ye baat batai. unhoney farmaya : meri shaadi ki subh Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye aur merey paas do ladkiyan geet ga rahi thin, aur (she'ron mein) merey un buzurgon ka zikr kar rahi thin jo jange-badar mein shaheed huye. wo jo she'r padh rahi thin un mein ye fiqra bhi tha : ( وَفِيْنَا نَبِيٌّ يَعْلَمُ ما فِي غَدٍ ) hamarey andar eik Nabi hai jo janta hai kal kya honey wala hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye baat na kaho . kal ki baaten Allah key siwa koi nahin janta ."
1898,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) merey paas tashrif laye to merey paas ansaar ki do ladkiyan, wo sher tarannum sey padh rahi thin jo ansariyon ney jange-Buaas key moqey par eik doosrey key khilaf kahey they. wo (peshawar) gaaney waliyan nahin thin. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney (ye haal dekh kar) farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar mein shetani raag ka kya kaam ? ye eidul-fitr ka din tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : abu-Bakar ! har qom ki eik eid hoti hai, aur aaj hamari eid hai."
1899,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina key eik hissey (eik mohalley ya gali) sey guzrey to dekha ke kuch bachchiyaan daf baja baja kar ga rahi thin aur keh rahi thin : ( نَحْنُ جَوَارٍ مِنْ بَنِي النَّجَّارِ . . . يَا حَبَّذَا مُحَمَّدٌ مِنْ جَارِ ) hum qabila banu Najjar ki ladkiyan hain (aur hamen khushi hai ke) Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( hamarey) kitney achey hamsaaey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah janta hai ke main tum sey mohabbat rakhta hun .
1900,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney apni eik rishte daar Ansari ladki ki shaadi ki. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur farmaya : tum logon ney ladki ko rukhsat kar diya ? unhoney kaha : ji haan . farmaya : kya tum ney uskey sath kisi ko bheja hai jo geet gaey ? ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) kaha : ji nahin . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ansaar log geet waghera pasand kartey hain. ( behtar hota) agar tum uskey sath ( kisi ko) bhejtey jo kehta : ( أَتَيْنَاكُمْ أَتَيْنَاكُمْ فَحَيَّانَا وَحَيَّاكُمْ ) hum tumharey paas aaye hain. hum tumharey paas aaye hain. hamen bhi Mubarak, tumhen bhi Mubarak ."
1901,"Hazrat Mujahid (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key sath tha ke unhen dhol ki aawaz sunai di . unhoney kanon mein ungliyan dey lin aur (raastey sey) eik taraf hat gaey. (taake aawaz sey ziyada door ho jaeyn.) unhoney teen baar aisa hi kya. phir farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi isi tarah kya tha."
1902,"Hazrat Zenab bint Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ( apni walida) ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaati hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas tashrif laye to (ghar mein) eik mukhannas ko Abdullah bin Abu-Umaiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye kehtey suna : agar Allah ney kal Taaif ki Fateh nasib farmaai to main tujhey eik aurat dikhaaunga jo (itni moti hai ke) aati hai to chaar bal padtey (nazar aatey) hain, jati hai to aath bal padtey (nazar aatey) hain. (bahut moti aur khub surat hai.) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey gharon sey nikal do."
1903,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mardon sey mushaabihat ikhtiyar karney wali aurat par, aur aurton sey mushaabihat ikhtiyar karney waley mard par lanat farmaai hai."
1904,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aurton sey mushaabihat ikhtiyar karney waley mardon par aur mardon sey mushaabihat ikhtiyar karney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai.
1905,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab shaadi ki Mubarak baad detey to yun farmatey : ( بَارَكَ اللَّهُ لَكُمْ , وَبَارَكَ عَلَيْكُمْ , وَجَمَعَ بَيْنَكُمَا فِي خَيْرٍ ) Allah tumhen barkat dey , aur tum par barkat nazil farmaai , aur tum dono ko khair mein ikhatta kerey."
1906,"Hazrat Aqeel bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney qabila banu Jasham ki eik khatoon sey shaadi ki, logon ney (Mubarak baad key tor par) kaha : ( بِالرَّفَاءِ , وَالْبَنِينَ ) tumhari aapas mein muwaafiqat ho aur betey nasib hon. Hazrat Aqeel (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : is tarah na kaho balke jis tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai is tarah kaho : ( اللَّهُمَّ بَارِكْ لَهُمْ , وَبَارِكْ عَلَيْهِمْ ) ya-Allah! unhen barkat dey aur un par barkat nazil farma."
1907,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu)) key libas ( par zardi ka nishan dekha to farmaya : ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey eik guthlii bhar soney (haq mehar) par eik khatoon sey nikah kar liya hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : waleema karo, chahey eik bakri hi ho."
1908,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey nahin dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi zauja mohtarma sey nikah key moqey par aisa (pur takalluf) waleema kya ho jaisa Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) sey nikah key moqey par kya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (us moqey par) eik bakri zibeh farmaai."
1909,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ka walima sattuon aur khajuron sey kya.
1910,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key eik waleemey mein hazir huwa . is mein na gosht tha aur na roti. (sirf sattu aur khajuren waghera pesh ki gaeen.) Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko sirf ibn Uena hi bayan kartey hain."
1911,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha aur Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya ke Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko tayyar karen taake unhen Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan rukhsat karen. hamney ghar ki taraf tawajjoh ki. aur is mein Bat'haa key maidan ki naram mitti bichha di (is tarah kamrey key naahamwaar farsh mein jo kankar patthar they, chhup gaey). phir hamney do takiyon mein khajoor key darkht ka chhilka bhara jisey hamney khud apney haathon sey dhuna tha, phir hamney khaney ko khajuren aur kishmish pesh ki aur peeney ko mitha pani pesh kiya. aur hamney eik lakdi ley kar kamrey key eik koney mein laga di taake is par mishkeeza aur kapdey latkaaey ja saken. hamney Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ki shaadi sey achchhi koi shaadi nahin dekhi."
1912,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Hazrat abu-Usaid (Abdullah bin Sabit) Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni shaadi key moqey par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dawat di. dulhan khud un ki khidmat kar rahi thi. unhoney farmaya : kya tumhen malum hai mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein kya mashrub pesh kiya? mainey raat ko kuchh khajuren pani mein dal den. subah ko mainey unhen saaf kiya aur yehi mashrub aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein nosh farmaney key liye pesh kar diya."
1913,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya is waleemey ka khana bad tareen khana hai jis mein dolat mandon ko bulaya jaey aur gharibon ko na bulaya jaey. aur jisney (waleeme ki dawat) qubul na ki, usney Allah ki aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki."
1914,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ko shaadi key waleemey mein bulaya jaey to usey chahiye ke (dawat) qubul karey."
1915,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pehley din waleema haq (zaruri) hai, doosrey din neki hai, teesrey din dikhawa aur shohrat hai."
1916,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sayiba key liye teen din raat ki muddat hai aur kunwaari key liye saat din raat."
1917,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jab Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anhuma) sey shaadi ki to teen din unkey yahan thehrey, phir farmaya : terey khawind (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nazar mein tera maqam kam nahin. agar to chahey to saat din terey paas thahroon . aur agar main saat din terey paas thehra to dusri biwiyon key paas bhi saat saat din thahroonga."
1918,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ko aurat ya londi ya janwer hasil ho to uskey sar key agley hissey ko pakad kar kahey : (اللهم إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ مِنْ خَيْرِهَا وَخَيْرِ ما جُبِلَتْ عَلَيْهِ وَأَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ شَرِّهَا وَشَرِّ ما جُبِلَتْ عَلَيْهِ),''aey Allah ! main tujh sey iski bhalai, aur iski paidaayshi aadaton ki bhalai maangta hun, aur iskey shar sey aur iski paidaayshi aadaton key shar sey teri panah mein aata hun."
1919,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi apni aurat key paas jata hai, agar us waqt ye alfaz keh ley : (اللهم جَنِّبْنِي الشَّيْطَانَ وَجَنِّبِ الشَّيْطَانَ ما رَزَقْتَنِي),''aey Allah ! mujh sey shetan ko door rakh aur to mujhey jo aulad dey, us sey bhi shetan ko door rakh.''phir agar unhen aulad mil gaee to Allah is par shetan ko musallat nahin kerega. ya farmaya : usey shetan nuqsan nahin pahunchaeyga."
1920,"Hazrat Behaz bin Hakim apney walid Hazrat Hakim bin Muawiya (Rahimahullah) aur wo (apney walid) Behaz key dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qushairi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aa'zaaey mastura (guptango) mein sey hamen kis chiz key zahir karney ki ijazat hai aur kis chiz ki mumaaniat hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : biwi aur londi key siwa sab sey apni sharmgaah ko mehfooz rakh. mainey arz kiya : ye irshad farmaiye ke agar log ikhattey hon (ya ikhattey rehtey hun)? farmaya : agar ye mumkin ho ke usey koi na dekhey to hergiz kisi ki nazar is par na padney dey. mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! agar koi akela ho? farmaya : tab bhi logon sey ziyada Allah ka haq hai ke us sey sharam ki jaey."
1921,"Hazrat Utba bin Abd Sulami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi apni biwi key paas jaey to usey chahiye ke parda karey , aur gadhon ki tarah nanga na ho jaey."
1922,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kabhi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sharmgah nahin dekhi. Abu-Bakar ney kaha : Abu Nuaim (Hazrat Aaisha key ghulam ki bajaey) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki londi sey bayan kiya kartey they."
1923,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us mard ki taraf nazar nahin farmaeyga , jo apni biwi sey peeth mein mujaamiat (sambhog) karta hai."
1924,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen baar farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala haq baat sey nahin sharmata. phir farmaya : aurton sey un ki peethon mein mujaamiat (sambhog) na karo."
1925,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Yahudi kaha kartey they ke jo koi pichhli taraf sey ho kar aurat sey agli jagah mein mubashrat (sambhog) karta hai, uska beta bhengaa paida hota hai to Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di : (نِسَآؤُكُمْ حَرْثٌ لَّكُمْ فَأْتُوا۟ حَرْثَكُمْ أَنَّىٰ شِئْتُمْ),''tumhari biwiyan tumhari khetiyan hain. apni kheton mein jis tarah chaho aao.''"
1926,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey azl (sambhog ke waqt mard ka apne khas ang ka aurat key khas ang se baahir nikalna khas waqt mein) ke barey mein sawal kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum ye kaam kartey ho? agar na karo to koi harj nahin, jis rooh ko paida karney ka Allah ney faisla kar liya hai, wo ho kar rahegi."
1927,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein hum log azl (sambhog ke waqt mard ka apne khas ang ka aurat key khas ang se baahir nikalna khas waqt mein) kar liya kartey they jabke Quran nazil ho raha tha."
1928,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney azad aurat sey uski ijazat key baghair azl kerney (sambhog ke waqt mard ka apne khas ang ka aurat key khas ang se baahir nikalna khas waqt mein) sey mana farmaya."
1929,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi aurat sey , uski phuphi ya khaala key nikah mein hotey huye nikah na kiya jaey."
1930,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko do nikaahon sey mana farmatey huye suna hai, (is baat sey mana farmaya) ke koi mard eik aurat aur uski phuphi ko (nikah mein) jama kerey. ya aurat aur uski khaala ko (nikah mein jama karey)."
1931,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat sey , uski phuphi ya khaala key nikah mein hotey huye nikah na kiya jaey."
1932,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Rifaa Qurzi (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kiya : main Rifaa Qurzi (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thi. usney mujhey Talaq dey di aur bitta Talaq (aakhiri Talaq) bhi dey daali. (uskey baad) mainey Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber sey nikah kar liya. (lekin) unkey paas to jo kuchh hai wo kapdey key sirey ki tarah hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : tum dobara Rifaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey nikah karna chahti ho? nahin, nahin  (ye nahin ho sakta) yahan tak key to us (Abdur-Rehman) sey lazzat hasil karey aur wo tujh sey lazzat hasil karey."
1933,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us shakhs key barey mein farmaya jis key nikah mein koi aurat ho, wo usey Talaq dey dey, phir us aurat sey koi aur mard nikah kar key khilwat (tanhaai) sey pehley Talaq dey dey, kya wo dobara pehley mard sey nikah kar sakti hai? (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ) nahin, jab tak us (doosrey mard) sey lazzat hasil na karey."
1934,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney halala karney waley aur halala karaney waley par lanat farmaai hai."
1935,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney halala karney waley aur halala karaney waley par lanat farmaai hai."
1936,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main kiraaey key saand key mutalliq na bataun (ke wo kon hota hai)? Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : ji haan (bataiye) aey Allah key Rasool ! farmaya : wo halala karney wala hai, Allah ney halala karney waley aur halala karaney waley (dono) par lanat farmaai hai."
1937,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : razaat (doodh pilaane) sey bhi wo (rishta) haram ho jata hai jo nasab sey haram hota hai."
1938,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey Hazrat Hamza bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti key barey mein darkhaast ki gaee (ke un sey nikah farma lein). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo merey razaai (doodh shareek) bhai ki beti hai aur jo nasab sey haram hota hai wo razaat (doodh pilaane) sey bhi haram ho jata hai.
1939,"Hazrat Zenab binte Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya ke unhon (Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha)) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : meri hamsheera (bahan) Azza sey nikah farma lijiye. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tujhey ye baat pasand hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan, Allah key Rasool ! main aap key paas akeli to nahin, hun (ke saukan ki mojudgi pasand na karun) aur khair o barkat mein meri sharaakat ka haq sab sey ziyada meri behan ko hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to merey liye jayez nahin. unhoney kaha : hum log baaten kartey hain (sunney mein aaya hai) ke aap Darra binte Abu-Salma sey nikah karney waley hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Abu-Salma ki beti sey? kaha : ji haan. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar wo merey ghar mein parwarish paney wali (soteli) beti na hoti, tab bhi merey liye halal na hoti. wo to doodh key rishtey sey meri bhatiji hai. mujhey aur uskey walid ko Saubiya ney doodh pilaya tha. tum merey liye apni behnon aur betiyon ki peshkash na kiya karo. Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey yehi riwayat eik dusri sanad sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1940,"Hazrat Umme al-Fazal (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik baar doodh peena haram nahin karta, na do baar doodh peena, na eik baar choosnaa, na do baar choosnaa."
1941,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik do baar choosnaa haram nahin karta.
1942,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah Taala ney Quran Majeed mein jo kuch nazil farmaya, phir uski tilawat mansookh ho gaee, is mein ye bhi tha ke das baar doodh pilaney, ya paanch baar doodh pilaney hi sey mehram ka rishta qaaim hota hai."
1943,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Sahla binte Suhel (Raziallahu anha) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab Salim merey yahaan aatey hain to mujhey (apney shohar) Hazrat abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) key chehrey par nagawari key aasaar nazar aatey hain to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey doodh pila do. unhoney kaha : main usey kis tarah doodh pilaaun, wo to jawan aadmi hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : mujhey malum hai ke wo jawan aadmi hai.  Sahla‬ (Raziallahu anha) ney aisey hi kiya. (baad mein) wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : uskey baad mainey Hazrat abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) key chehrey par wo taasuraat nahin dekhey jo mujhey nagawar hon. Hazrat abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) jange-badar mein shareek they."
1944,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat aur badi umr key ladkey ko das baar doodh pilaney key masle par mushtamil aayat nazil hui thi. ye dono aayaten eik kaghaz par likhi hui merey bistar par padi thin. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui, hum aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghusl aur kafan waghera mein mashghool ho gaey. eik bakri aai aur wo kaghaz kha gaee."
1945,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas tashrif laye to unkey paas eik mard betha tha. aap ney farmaya : ye kon hai? unhoney kaha : ye mera bhai hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghor kar liya karo ke tum kisey apney paas aaney ki ijazat dey rahi ho kyonkey doodh pilane se rishte ki hurmat bhook mein doodh pilane se hoti hai.
1946,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : razaat (doodh pilana) wohi (moatabar) hai jo aanton ko phaadey."
1947,"Hazrat Zenab binte Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tamam azwaaje mutah'raat (paak biwiyon) Raziallahu anhu anhunna ney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey ikhtilaf kiya, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huzaifa key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ki si razaat (doodh pilaane) ki bina par kisi ko apney paas aaney ki ijazat nahin di. (aisey afrad sey parda kiya) aur farmaya : kya malum shayad ye ijazat sirf Hazrat Salim (Raziallahu anhu) key liye makhsus ho."
1948,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey razaai (doodh shareek) chacha Hazrat Aflah bin Abu-Qaees (Raziallahu anhu) ney aa kar mujh sey andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki, us waqt pardey ka hukm nazil ho chuka tha. chunanche mainey ijazat deney sey inkar kar diya yahan tak key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye. (mainey waqia arz kiya) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo terey chacha hain, unhen ijazat do. mainey kaha : mujhey aurat ney doodh pilaya hai, mard ney to nahin pilaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : terey haath ko mitti lagey. ya terey daain haath ko mitti lagey."
1949,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey razaai (doodh shareek) chacha ney aa kar mujh sey andar aaney ki ijazat talab ki, mainey unhen ijazat deney sey inkar kar diya. (maloom honey par) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : terey chacha ko terey paas (ghar mein) aana chahiye. mainey kaha : mujhey aurat ney doodh pilaya hai, mard ney doodh nahin pilaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo terey chacha hain, unhen terey paas aana chahiye."
1950,"Hazrat Feeroz Dailmi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to merey nikah mein do behney thin jin sey mainey Zamanae-jahiliyat mein nikah kiya tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab wapis jao to un mein sey eik ko Talaq dey dena."
1951,"Hazrat Feeroz Dailmi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey Islam qubul kar liya hai aur merey nikah mein do behney hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey farmaya : un mein sey jis aurat ko chaho Talaq dey do."
1952,"Hazrat Qais bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Islam qubul kiya to merey nikah mein aath aurten thin. mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar ye baat batai to aap ney farmaya : un mein sey chaar aurten muntakhab kar (chun lo) lo."
1953,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Ghelaan bin Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ney Islam qubul kiya to unkey nikah mein das aurten thin. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : un mein sey chaar rakh lo."
1954,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo shartein puri ki janey ka haq sab sey ziyada rakhti hain, jinkey sath tum ney aurton ki ismat (apney liye) halal ki."
1955,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nikah sey qabl jo mehar, Atiya ya hiba waghera ki shart ho, wo aurat ka haq hai. aur jo nikah ho janey key baad ho, wo usi ka hai jis ko dey diya gaya. aur aadmi bahut haq rakhta hai ke uski beti ya behan ki wajeh sey uski izzat afzaai ki jaey (aur usey koi tohfa diya jaey)."
1956,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiski koi londi ho aur wo usey achchhey tareeqey sey adab tamiz sikhaey aur achchhi taalim dey, phir usey azad kar key us sey nikah kar ley, uskey liye do sawab hain. aur ehale kitab mein sey jo shakhs apney Nabi par eman laya aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par bhi eman laya, uskey liye do sawab hain aur wo ghulam insan jo apney zimmey Allah ka haq bhi ada karta hai aur apney malikon ka haq bhi ada karta hai, uskey liye do sawab hain. Imam Shaabey ney (apney shagrid ko ye hadees suna kar) farmaya : mainey tujhey ye hadees muft hi dey di hai, halanke is sey kam tar hadees key liye Madiney ka safar kiya jata tha."
1957,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Safeeya (Raziallahu anha) Hazrat Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) key hissey mein aai thin, baad mein wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko mil gaeen to aap ney un sey nikah kar liya aur un ki azadi ko unka haq mehar qarar diya. (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid) Abdul-Azeez ney (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key doosrey shagrid) Sabit sey kaha : Abu-Muhammad ! kya aap ney Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye daryaft kiya tha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Safeeya (Raziallahu anha) ko kya kuchh haq mehar mein diya? unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen mehar key tor par khud un ki zaat (ki azadi) ata farmaai thi."
1958,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Safeeya (Raziallahu anha) ko azad kiya aur un ki azadi ko unka haq mehar qarar dey kar un sey nikah kar liya.
1959,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab ghulam, apney aaqa ki ijazat key baghair nikah kar ley to wo bad kaar hai."
1960,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi ghulam apney malikon ki ijazat key baghair nikah karey, wo bad kaar hai."
1961,Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jange-khaibar key moqey par aurton sey mut'aa karney sey aur paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney sey mana farma diya tha.
1962,"Hazrat Rabee bin Sabra apney walid (Hazrat Sabra bin Maabad Juhni (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney farmaya : hum Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath rawana huye (raastey mein baaz) Sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey liye mujarrad (akele) rehna dushwaar ho gaya hai. aap ney farmaya : aurton sey mut'aa kar lo. hum aurton key paas gaey, unhoney muddat key ta'yun key baghair hum sey nikah karney sey inkar kiya. Sahaba ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey is baat ka zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : un sey muddat mutayyan kar lo. chunanche main aur mera eik chacha zaad (hum dono) rawana huye. uskey paas eik chadar thi aur merey paas bhi eik chadar thi. uski chadar meri chadar sey achchhi thi aur main us sey jawan tha. hum eik aurat key yahan pahunchey (aur us sey baat ki). usney kaha : chadar chadar barabar hai. chunanche mainey us sey nikah kar liya. aur us raat uskey yahaan thehra. subah hui to mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Kaabe key darwazey aur rukn key darmiyan khadey hain, aur farma rahey hain : logo ! mainey tumhen mut'aa ki ijazat di thi, suno ! Allah ney isey qiyamat tak key liye haram farma diya hai, lihaza jis key paas koi aisi aurat hai, wo usey azad kar dey. aur tum ney unhen jo kuchh diya hai, is mein sey kuchh bhi (wapis) na lo."
1963,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya : jab Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa huye to unhoney logon sey khitab farmaya. is mein unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen teen din tak mut'aa ki ijazat di thi, phir usey haram farma diya. qism hai Allah ki ! mujhey jis shakhs key barey mein mut'aa karney ki ittilaa milegi, agar wo shaadi shuda huwa to main usey patharon sey rajm karwa dunga. siwaye iskey ke wo chaar gawah ley kar aaye jo is baat ki gawahi den ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uski hurmat ka aelan karney key baad usey halal qarar dey diya tha."
1964,"Hazrat Yazeed bin Asamm (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujh sey Ummul-mominin Hazrat Memuna binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan farmaya ke jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey nikah kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) halal they (ehraam ki haalat mein nahin they). Hazrat Yazeed bin Asamm (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) meri bhi khaala thin aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ki bhi khaala thin."
1965,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ehraam ki haalat mein nikah kiya.
1966,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ehraam wala khud apna nikah kar sakta hai na kisi doosrey ka nikah kar sakta hai aur na nikah ka pegham hi dey sakta hai."
1967,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tumharey paas aisa aadmi (rishta maangney) aaye, jis ka akhlaq aur Deen tumhen pasand ho to usey rishta dey do. agar tum yun nahin karogey to zamin mein bahut ziyada fitna aur fasad paida ho jaeyga."
1968,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : husoole aulad key liye (achchhi aurten) muntakhab (chuna) karo, hum martaba logon sey rishtey lo aur do."
1969,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiski do aurten hon aur wo eik ko dusri par tarjeeh dey, wo qiyamat key din us haal mein aayega ke uska aadha jism gira huwa (mafiooj) hoga."
1970,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar mein tashrif ley jatey to apni biwiyon key darmiyan qura-andazi kartey they.
1971,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni biwiyon mein baari muqarrar kartey they, aur (is mamley mein) insaf sey kaam letey they, phir farmatey they : aey Allah ! jo kuchh merey bas mein hai us mein, main ye kaam karta hun. meri us mamley mein muwaakhiza (poochh gachh) na farmana jo terey bas mein hai, merey bas mein nahin, yani dili mohabbat."
1972,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Hazrat Sauda binte Zamaa (Raziallahu anha) umr Raseeda ho gaeen to unhoney apna din Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko bakhsh diya, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ka din bhi Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari mein shumar kartey they."
1973,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hazrat Safiya binte Hayi (Raziallahu anha) ki koi baat nagawar guzri (chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney be rukhi ka izhar farmaya). Hazrat Safeeya (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : aey Aaisha ! kya tum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko mujh sey razi kar sakti ho? aur mera (eik) din tumhara huwa. unhoney kaha : haan. chunanche Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney za'fraan sey rangi hui apni eik odhni li. is par pani chhidkaa taake khushbu mehak uthey, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key qarib aa bethein to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Aaisha ! parey raho, aaj tumhari baari ka din nahin. unhoney kaha : (ذٰلِكَ فَضْلُ اللهِ . . .), ''ye Allah ka Fazal hai jisey chahta hai ata kar deta hai.'' aur puri baat batai. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Safeeya (Raziallahu anhu) sey razi ho gaey."
1974,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ye aayat mubaarka (وَٱلصُّلْحُ خَيْرٌ), ''aur suleh behtar hai.'' us shakhs key barey mein nazil hui hai jis key nikah main eik aurat thi, jo taweel (lamba) arsa uskey sath rahi, aur us sey us mard ki aulad bhi hui, phir (jab wo boodhi ho gaee to) mard ney chaha ke us ko chhod kar kisi dusri aurat sey nikah kar ley. aurat ney usey is baat par razi kar liya ke wo usi key nikah mein rahegi, wo usey baari na dey (usney kaha : main apni baari chhodti hun, Talaq na den)."
1975,"Hazrat Abu-Raham (Ehzaab bin Usaid) (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey afzal sifarish ye hai ke do afrad key maa-bain nikah key liye sifarish ki jaey."
1976,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghar ki chaukhat sey thokar lagi, unkey chehrey par zakham aa gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uska khoon saaf kar do. mujhey is sey karaahat mehsus hui. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khud unkey chehrey sey khoon pochhney aur saaf karney lagey, phir farmaya : agar Usama ladki hota to main usey zewar pehnaata aur kapdey pehnaata, phir uski shaadi kar deta."
1977,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtar wo hai jo apney ghar walon key liye behtar ho aur tum sab ki nisbat main apney ghar walon key liye behtar hun."
1978,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtar wo log hain, jo apni aurton key liye behtar hain."
1979,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey daud lagai to main aap sey aagey nikal gaee."
1980,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (jange-khaibar sey wapis) Madina tashrif laye to aap Hazrat Safiya binte Hayi (Raziallahu anha) key dulhaa baney. ansaar ki aurten aayen, unhoney mujhey Safiya (Raziallahu anha) (key husn aur jamaal) key barey mein bataya. main bhes badal kar naqaab pehan kar (dulhan ko dekhney) chali gaee. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko meri aankh nazar aai to aap ney mujhey pehchan liya. aur meri taraf mutawajjeh huye. main tezi sey chali (ghar sey bahar nikalney lagi) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey aa liya aur mujhey aagosh mein ley liya. aur farmaya : tum ney (dulhan ko) kaisa paya? mainey kaha : chhodiye ! Yahudi aurton mein sey eik aurat hai."
1981,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mujhey pata bhi na chala yahan tak key Zenab (Raziallahu anha) baghair ijazat hi merey hujrey mein aa gaeen, wo (us waqt) bahut ghussey mein thin. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab Abu-Bakar ki bachchi aap key samney nanhey-nanhey bazu hilaati hai to kya aap ko yehi baat kafi hoti hai? phir wo meri taraf mutawajjeh huin (aur ghussay ka izhar karney lagin) mainey munh pher liya. (aur un ki baaton ka koi jawab na diya ke kahin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko nagawar na guzrey). yahan tak key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum bhi badla ley lo. main un ki taraf palti (aur khub jawab diya) yahan tak key mainey dekha ke unkey munh mein lu'aab khushk ho gaya hai aur wo meri baaton ka koi jawab nahin dey rahi hain, mainey dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak chamak raha tha."
1982,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main us waqt bhi gudiyon sey khelaa karti thi jab main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa chuki thi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri saheliyon ko merey paas bhej detey they aur wo merey sath kheltin."
1983,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zamaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba diya. (mukhtalif masaayel bayan farmaaey) phir aurton ka zikr farmaya to unkey barey mein logon ko nasihat ki, phir farmaya : aadmi kab tak apni aurat ko londi ki tarah peet'ta rahega? shayad din key aakhir mein wo uskey sath letey."
1984,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney na apney kisi londi ghulam ko maara, na kabhi kisi biwi ko maara. (balke) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath sey kisi chiz ko nahin maara."
1985,"Hazrat Ayas bin Abdullah bin Abu-Zubab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki bandiyon ko hergiz na maaro. (chand din baad) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aurten apney khaawindon key samney jur'at dikhaney lagi hain (aur gustaakh ho gaee hain). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen maarney ki ijazat dey di. chunanche unhen maar padi. tab bahut si aurton ney aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (azwaaj mutah'raat (paak biwiyon) Raziallahu anhu anhunna) key yahan chakkar lagaey (aur paak biwiyon Raziallahu anhu anhunna sey apney khaawindon ki shikaayten kin). subah ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aaj raat aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (key yahan sattar aurten aayen. har aurat apney khawind ki shikayat kar rahi thi. tum dekho ! aisey log achchhey nahin hain."
1986,"Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik raat Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan mehman raha. aadhi raat hui to wo uth kar apni aurat ko maarney lagey, mainey beech bachao kara diya. jab wo apney bistar par gaey to mujh sey farmaya : aey Ash'as ! meri eik baat yad rakhna. mainey wo baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai. (aap ney farmaya :) mard sey nahin poochhnaa chahiye ke usney apni aurat ko kyon maara. aur witr padhey baghair mat soyaa kar. aur teesri baat mujhey yad nahin rahi. Hazrat Abu-Awaana (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey bhi mazkura baala riwayat ki maanind bayan kiya."
1987,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat bayan ki ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney baalon mein doosrey baal milaaney wali, aur baal milwaane wali aur godney wali aur gudwaaney wali par lanat farmaai hai."
1988,"Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : meri beti dulhan hai (uski shaadi qarib hai). usey chechak nikal aai hai aur baal jhad gaey hain to kya main uskey baalon mein doosrey baal mila dun? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney lanat ki hai baal milaaney wali aur milwane wali par."
1989,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney godney waaliyon par , gudwaaney waaliyon par , baal nochne waaliyon par , husn key liye daanton key darmiyan fasla paida karney waaliyon par aur Allah ki takhleeq mein tabdili karney waaliyon par lanat farmaai hai. qabila banu Asad ki eik khatoon , jinka naam Umme Yaqub tha, ko ye baat malum hui to wo Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : mujhey malum huwa hai ke aap ney ye ye baat farmaai hai. unhoney kaha : main is par kyon na lanat karun jis par Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney lanat farmaai hai, aur ye baat Allah ki kitab mein mojud hai. usney kaha : mainey to shuru sey aakhir tak sara Quran padha huwa hai. mujhey to (is mein) ye masla nahin mila. unhoney farmaya : agar tu ney (Quran) padha hota to tujhey (ye masla) mil jata. kya tu ney ye nahin padha : ( وَمَآ ءَاتَىٰكُمُ ٱلرَّسُولُ فَخُذُوهُ وَمَا نَهَىٰكُمْ عَنْهُ فَٱنتَهُوا۟ ),''Rasool tumhen jo kuchh den wo ley lo aur jis sey mana karen, us sey ruk jao.'' usney kaha : ji haan (ye to padha hai). farmaya : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un kamon sey mana farmaya hai. usney kaha : mera khayal hai ke aap key ghar waley ye kaam kartey hain. unhoney farmaya : jao , ja kar dekh lo. usney ja kar dekha to usey koi aisi baat nazar na aai jo wo dekhna chahti thi. usney (wapis aa kar) kaha : mujhey to koi baat nazar nahin aai. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : agar wo baat isi tarah hoti jis tarah to kehti thi to wo (biwi) hamarey sath na rehti."
1990,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey Shawwaal mein nikah farmaya, aur Shawwaal hi mein mujhey (rukhsati kara key) apney ghar laye, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kon si zauja (biwi) mohtarma ko mujh sey ziyada Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qurbat hasil thi? (Hazrat Urwa ney farmaya : ) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) apney kunbey ki aurton ki rukhsati shawwaal mein karna pasand karti thin."
1991,Hazrat Abdul-Malik bin Haris bin Hisham apney walid (Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris bin Hisham) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey Shawwaal mein nikah kiya aur Shawwaal mein unhen (rukhsati kara key) ghar laaye.
1992,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen hukm diya ke khawind key paas uski biwi ko bhej den, halanke usney abhi usey koi chiz nahin di thi."
1993,"Hazrat Makhmar bin Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna ke aap farma rahey they : nahusat kuchh nahin aur barkat baaz oqaat teen chizon mein hoti hai : aurat mein , ghodey mein aur makaan mein."
1994,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nahusat key barey mein farmaya : agar ho to ghodey , aurat ya ghar mein hoti hai."
1995,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahusat teen chizon mein hai : ghodey mein , aurat mein aur makaan mein. eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney ye teen cheezen shumar kar key, unkey sath (chauthi chiz) talwaar ka bhi zikr karti thin."
1996,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik ghairat Allah ko pasand hai, aur eik ghairat Allah ko na pasand hai. jo ghairat Allah ko pasand hai wo kharabi key aasaar malum honey par ghairat hai aur jo ghairat Allah ko na pasand hai, wo kharabi key aasaar key baghair (chahey khaahme khaa) ghairat karna hai."
1997,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey kisi aurat par is tarah rashk mehsus nahin huwa jis qadr Hazrat Khadeeja (Raziallahu anha) sey rashk mehsus huwa kyonkey mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen kasrat sey yad kartey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Rab ney hukm diya tha ke Hazrat Khadeeja (Raziallahu anha) ko jannat mein moti key mehal ki khush khabri den. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : is sey murad soney ka mehal hai."
1998,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima bin Naufal (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna jabke aap member par tashrif farma they : Hisham bin Mughira key beton ney mujh sey ijazat talab ki hai ke wo apni beti ka nikah Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey kar den. main unhen ijazat nahin deta, phir (kehta hun ke) main unhen ijazat nahin deta, phir (kehta hun ke) main unhen ijazat nahin deta, haan agar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bin Abi Talib ye pasand karen ke meri beti (Fatima (Raziallahu anha)) ko Talaq dey kar un ki ladki sey shaadi kar lein (to un ki marzi hai). Fatima (Raziallahu anha)  to mera tukda (merey jism aur jaan ka eik hissa) hai. jis baat sey usey pareshani hoti hai us sey mujhey bhi pareshani hoti hai. jis baat sey usey dukh pahunchta hai, us sey mujhey bhi dukh pahunchta hai."
1999,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ney Abu-Jahal ki beti ka rishta talab kiya jabke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Hazrat Fatima unkey nikah mein thin. jab Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney ye baat suni to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : log baaten kartey hain ke aap ko apni betiyon key mutalliq kisi baat par ghussa nahin aata. ye (dekhiye) Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Jahal ki beti sey nikah karney waley hain. Hazrat Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye, mainey suna ke aap ney tashahud padha (khutbe key shuruaati kalimaat irshad farmaaey) phir farmaya : ama'-baad , mainey Abul-Aas bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) ko rishta diya. unhoney mujh sey (jo bhi) baat ki, sachchi baat ki. aur be-shak Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima (Raziallahu anha) mera tukda (aur meri lakhte jigar) hai. mujhey ye baat achchhi nahin lagti ke tum usey aazmaaish mein dalo. qism hai Allah ki ! Allah key Rasool ki beti aur Allah key dushman ki beti kabhi eik aadmi key paas (uskey nikah mein) jama nahin hongi. Raavi ney bayan kiya : chunanche Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) us rishtey sey dast bardar ho gaey."
2000,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, wo kaha karti thin : kya aurton ko sharam nahin aati ke wo apne aap Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hiba karti hain? to Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di : ( تُرْجِى Man تَشَآءُ مِنْهُنَّ وَتُـْٔوِىٓ إِلَيْكَ Man تَشَآءُ ),''un mein sey jisey aap chahen (us sey mulaqat ko) muakhkhar kar (taal) den aur jisey chahen apney qarib kar lein.'' Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : tab mainey kaha : (Allah key Rasool) aap ka Rab aap ki khahish foran puri farma deta hai."
2001,"Hazrat Sabit (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bethey they. un ki eik beti bhi mojud thin. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur usney apney aap ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (sey nikah) key liye pesh kiya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ko meri khahish hai? Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti ney kaha : wo kitni be sharam thi ! Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wo tujh sey afzal thi. usney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mohabbat ki wajeh sey apni zaat ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya."
2002,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila banu Fazara key eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri aurat ney saanwla ladka jana hai. (aur main to goraa hun) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya terey paas oont hain? usney kaha : ji haan. farmaya : wo kis rang key hain? usney kaha : surkh hain. farmaya : kya un mein koi khaaki rang ka bhi hai? usney kaha : (ji haan), un mein khaaki rang key bhi hain. farmaya : un mein ye rang kahan sey aa gaya. usney kaha : shayad kisi rag ney zor kiya hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shayad us (ladkey) mein bhi kisi rag ney zor kiya ho. ye alfaz (hadees ke raawi) ibne Sabaah key hain."
2003,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik khana-badosh Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri aurat key yahan, merey nikah mein rehtey huye, siyah faam (rang) ladka paida huwa hai aur hamarey khandan mein kabhi koi siyah faam (rang) nahin tha (hamarey nanihaal aur dadhihaal sab safed faam (rang) hain). to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya terey paas oont hain? usney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : wo kis rang key hain? kaha : surkh hain. aap ney farmaya : kya un mein koi siyah bhi hai? usney kaha : ji nahin. farmaya : kya un mein koi khaaki rang ka bhi hai? usney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : wo kaisey ho gaya? usney kaha : shayad kisi (dada pardada ya nana waghera) ka khoon ghalib aaya hai? farmaya : shayad tumharey us betey par bhi kisi ka khoon ghalib aa gaya hai."
2004,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Zamaa ki londi sey paida honey waley eik ladkey key barey mein Hazrat Abd bin Zamaa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) apna jhagda ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! jab main Makka gaya tha to merey bhai ney mujhey nasihat ki thi ke main Zamaa ki londi key bachchey ko dekh kar apni kafalat mein ley lun. Hazrat Abd bin Zamaa (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : wo mera bhai hai, merey walid ki kaneez ka beta hai. merey walid key ghar mein paida huwa hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dekha ke wo (ladka) Utba sey mushaabihat rakhta hai to farmaya : aey Abd bin Zamaa ! wo tumhara bhai hai. bachcha bistar waley ka hota hai. aur aey Sauda ! tum is sey parda kiya karo."
2005,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla diya ke ladka bistar waley ka hai.
2006,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ladka bistar waley ka hai aur zaani key liye patthar hain."
2007,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : ladka bistar waley ka hai aur zaani key liye patthar hain."
2008,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar musalman ho gaee. us sey eik mard ney nikah kar liya. Raavi kehtey hain : baad iske uska pehla khawind aa gaya. usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main uskey sath hi musalman huwa tha aur usey merey musalman honey ka ilm tha. to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us aurat ko doosrey khawind sey juda kar key pehley khawind key paas bhej diya.
2009,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni beti (Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha)) ko do saal key baad, pehley nikah ki bina par hi, Hazrat Abul-Aas bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) key paas wapis bhej diya."
2010,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (apni beti) Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ko Hazrat Abul-Aas bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) key paas naya nikah kar key wapis bheja.
2011,"Hazrat Judaama binte Wahab Asadiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : mainey chaha tha ke tumhen ghailaa (doodh pilaney wali aurat sey hum bistar honey) sey mana kar dun. mainey dekha ke ehale Faras aur ehale Rome ghaiyaal kartey hain to unkey bachchey nahin martey (un key bachchon ko nuqsan nahin hota). aur mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna jabke aap sey azl (mard ka apne khas ang ko sakhlan ke waqt aurat ki shamgaah se baahir nikalne) key barey mein sawal kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : ye zinda qabr mein dafn karney ki poshida surat hai."
2012,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazeed bin Sakan (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni aulad ko khufiya tor par qatl na karo. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! ghailaa (doodh pilaney wali aurat sey hum bistar hona) to ghodey ki peeth par bethey huye sawar par bhi asar andaz ho kar usey gira deta hai."
2013,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik khatoon Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui uskey sath uskey do bachchey they. usney eik ko (god mein) uthaya huwa tha aur eik ko haath sey pakad kar liye aa rahi thi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (ye dekh kar) farmaya : (ye aurten bachchon ko) uthaney wali  jan'ne wali aur reham karney wali hoti hain, agar unka apney khaawindon sey na munasib sulook na ho to un mein sey jo namaz ki paband hain, wo jannat mein dakhil ho jaaeyn."
2014,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi aurat apney khawind ko eza (takleef) deti hai to (jannat ki) hooron mein sey us mard ki biwi (hoor) kehti hai : Allah tujhey tabah karey ! is shakhs ko takleef na dey, ye to terey paas mehman hai anqarib tujhey chhod kar hamarey paas aaney wala hai."
2015,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haram kaam halal ko haram nahin karta."
